1. Maximum subarray problem:
a) kadane's algorithm:
  curr_max = max(A[i], cur_max+A[i]);
  overallmax = max(overallmax, curr_max);

2.  Maximum subarray in a circular array
a) calculate regular max sum using kadane
b) find minimum subarray and remaining elements yield a subarray that wraps around;
  Total sum - minimum subarray
c) max(a, b)  
